{"tid":1824310,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【測試】熱門新功能—行動篇","createTime":"2020-01-14T10:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T05:00:06.000Z","uid":259519,"like":132,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d4f0bc123fb4b5a544e312286282340a380489c1","tid":1824310,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T10:37:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">邊個留言，邊個就係鬼<br />\n不要回覆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n依個post我想嘗試重整連登軍心，<span style=\"color: gold;\">再次團結</span>一眾手足。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果你<span style=\"color: gold;\">未放棄香港</span>，堅持到底，對抗<span style=\"color: red;\">暴政</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">警暴</span>，以勝利換來手足的安息，請比<span style=\"color: blue;\">正評</span>。</span><br />\n<br />\n我係樓主，係我個人角度黎講，絕對有資格標籤你係<span style=\"color: red;\">鬼</span>。<br />\n不過，留唔留言，你有<span style=\"color: red;\">自由</span>，係你既選擇，post就係我開既，<span style=\"color: green;\">連登就係大家既</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不厭其煩我都要再強調一次，現實生活或者夢境，都<span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以亂咁/輕易捉鬼</span>，鬼係捉唔曬！但依到唔同，你無野輸，只有進步、新方法、不斷改善、重建、同團結，先可以令運動再重燃希望！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tcaCR1F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtcaCR1F.jpg&h=82402811&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">FIVE DEMANDS, NOT ONE LESS</span>"},{"pid":"47ab9bfa2eb580ff36f83c74e622fa0f1bdf8224","tid":1824310,"uid":228868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T10:38:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pZpgn8F.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpZpgn8F.gif&h=0d4648ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bca42cf6fc808c722c5613379c107a4c72ccaaff","tid":1824310,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T10:38:49.000Z","msg":"119 遮打道"},{"pid":"9aba1f8b9c4fbfa441d94f8b3d190eec1d12cabb","tid":1824310,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim